caption.p: The ( a) cytotoxicity and ( b) photocytotoxicity of the leaf extracts of the Clermont and Toogoolawah biotypes of parthenium weed against the murine fibroblasts. The log of the actual concentrations ranging from 0.008 to 0.25 mg mL −1 was taken to fit the linear regression curves. Error bars represent ± one standard error.
